name: puzzled
description: this abstract painting is a set of two 7" x 14" back stapled canvases.  original artwork is signed on the back so that you may hang in the direction you interpret the painting to go.  it is the perfect addition to any space that needs a pop of color.

name: dream big 2
description: standing among the giant trees the small mushroom really knows the importance of dreaming big.  maybe the mushroom will never reach that sort of height but that won't stop it from dreaming.  a whimsical reminder to never stop dreaming.  7" x 14" original acrylic painting on back stapled canvas, signature on side.
